\c 61
\s Mashoko omufaro anoparidzirwa Zioni
\p
\v 61 Mweya waIshe Jehovha uri pa- musoro pangu; nokuti Jehovha
\p akandizodza kuti ndiparidzire vanyoro mashoko akanaka; akandituma kuti ndirape vanemwoyo yakaputsika, kuti ndiparidzire vakatapwa kusunungurwa, nokuna vakasungwa kuti vachazarurirwa;
\v 2 kuti ndiparidzire gore rengoni dzaJehovha, nezuva rokutsiva raMwari wedu; kuti ndinyaradze vose vanochema;
\v 3 kuti ndigadzire vanochema paZioni vapiwe korona panzvimbo yamadota, mafuta omufaro panzvimbo yokuchema, nenguo yokurumbidza panzvimbo yomweya waziya; kuti vanzi miti yokururama, chakasimwa chaJehovha, kuti iye akudzwe.
\v 4 Ipapo vachavaka matongo akare, vachamutsazve nzvimbo dzakaparadzwa dzokutanga, vachagadzira maguta akanga aitwa matongo, nezvose zvakaparadzwa zvamarudzi namarudzi.
\v 5 Vatorwa vachamira vachifudza mapoka enyu amakwai, navaeni vachava varimi venyu navagadziri vemidzambiringa yenyu.
\v 6 Asi imi
