\p chakutumidzai vashumiri vaMwari wedu; muchadya pfuma yamarudzi avanhu, muchazvirumbidza nokukudzwa kwawo. Panzvimbo yokunyadziswa kwenyu, muchapiwa migove miviri; panzvimbo yokushorwa vachafarira mugove wavo; naizvozvo panyika yavo vachava nemigove miviri, vachava nomufaro usingaperi.
\v 8 Nokuti ini Jehovha ndinoda zvakarurama, ndinovenga kupamba pamwechete nezvakaipa; ndichaviripira zvirokwazvo, uye ndichaita sungano isingaperi navo.
\v 9 Vana vavo vachazikanwa pakati pamarudzi, nezvibereko zvavo pakati pavanhu; vose vanovaona vachavaziva, kuti ndirwo rudzi rwakaropafadzwa naJehovha.
\p
\v 10 Ndichafarira Jehovha kwazvo, mweya wangu uchava nomufaro munaMwari wangu; nokuti akandifukidza nguo dzoruponeso, akandipfekedza chokufuka chokururama, somuwani anoshonga korona, uye somwenga unozvishongedza noukomba hwake.
\v 11 Nokuti nyika sezvainobudisa miti yayo, nomunda sezvaunomeresa zvakadyarwamo, saizvozvo Ishe Jehovha achameresa kururama nokurumbidzwa pamberi pamarudzi ose.
